verbose_text: The expression of angptl1b, angptl2b, angptl3b, angptl4a, angptl4b, angptl7 and angptl9b was confirmed in sea bream skin and the abundance of the amplified transcripts were subsequently characterised in intact and regenerating skin by quantitative real-time PCR.
